  "title": "Public Relations Assistant (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Public Relations Assistant</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Manage and respond to feedback from residents and tenants affected by our projects</p>\n<p>- Conduct regular site visits to gather feedback and keep stakeholders informed of project updates</p>\n<p>- Perform administrative tasks and other duties as required</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>- Minimum 1 year HIP experience</p>\n<p>- Minimum GCE \"O\" Level for Assistant role</p>\n<p>- GCE \"A\" Level, Diploma, or Degree holders eligible for Officer role</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>How to Apply:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you're a team player with excellent communication skills, please submit your application, including:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Current and expected salary</p>\n<p>- Reason(s) for leaving your current role</p>\n<p>- Date of availability</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We thank all applicants for their interest; however, only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
